brands.title: Royal Canin
brands.description: Royal Canin is a global pet food brand founded in France in 1968. The company focuses on scientifically developed nutrition tailored to the specific needs of different dog and cat breeds, ages, and health conditions. Today, its products are widely recommended by veterinarians and sold around the world.

brands.title: Purina Pro Plan
brands.description: Purina Pro Plan is a premium pet food brand offering scientifically formulated nutrition for dogs and cats to support optimal health and wellbeing. Its products are recommended by veterinarians worldwide.

brands.title: Hill's Science Diet
brands.description: Hill's Science Diet is a premium pet food brand focused on scientifically developed nutrition for dogs and cats. Their products are designed to support health, longevity, and specific dietary needs, recommended by veterinarians globally.

brands.title: Orijen
brands.description: Orijen is a Canadian premium pet food brand known for biologically appropriate recipes using fresh, regional ingredients. Their products are designed to mimic the natural diet of dogs and cats, supporting optimal health and wellbeing.

brands.title: Acana
brands.description: Acana is a Canadian premium pet food brand that focuses on biologically appropriate nutrition for dogs and cats. Their recipes use fresh, regional ingredients to support overall health and vitality.

brands.title: Pedigree
brands.description: Pedigree is a globally recognized pet food brand providing balanced nutrition for dogs. Its products focus on health, growth, and wellbeing, making it a trusted choice for pet owners worldwide.
